<noinclude>
This template is used to display tutorial information boxes.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{TutorialInfo
|level=Beginner/Intermediate/Advanced
|duration=30 minutes
|prerequisites=None or list prerequisites
|topics=Comma-separated list of topics
}}
</pre>

== Example ==
{{TutorialInfo
|level=Beginner
|duration=30 minutes
|prerequisites=None
|topics=Account creation, Basic navigation
}}

